    <lcObjective>What is a topic?</lcObjective>
    <lcObjective>What kind of topics exist in DITA</lcObjective>
    <lcObjective>What information goes in different types of topics</lcObjective>
    <lcObjective>What are constraints and specialization?</lcObjective>
   </lcObjectivesGroup>
